sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Slack
    participant EH as Event Handler
    participant FC as File Collector
    participant PP as Processing Pipeline
    participant AG as Proposal Agent
    participant VDB as Vector Store
    participant FS as File System

    Note over S,FS: Phase 1 — File Ingestion
    S->>EH: file_shared event (WebSocket)
    EH->>FC: enqueue collect task
    FC->>S: download file (bot token)
    FC->>FS: save to data/raw/
    FC->>FC: classify (document or qa_answer)
    FC->>PP: enqueue processing job

    Note over S,FS: Phase 2 — Document Processing (background)
    PP->>FS: read from data/raw/
    PP->>PP: extract text (parser by type)
    PP->>PP: LLM → clean Markdown (Haiku)
    PP->>FS: save to data/clean/
    PP->>PP: chunk (heading-aware)
    PP->>VDB: embed + upsert chunks

    Note over S,FS: Phase 3 — Proposal Generation
    S->>EH: app_mention — "create proposal" (WebSocket)
    EH->>AG: enqueue agent task
    AG->>VDB: search_workspace_docs(requirement)
    AG->>VDB: search_common_knowledge(requirement)
    AG->>AG: gap analysis (LLM — Sonnet)
    alt info missing
        AG->>FS: generate_qa_excel → save to data/raw/
        AG->>S: post Q&A file to Slack
        S->>EH: file_shared (answered Excel, WebSocket)
        EH->>FC: collect → classify as qa_answer
        FC->>AG: trigger QA evaluation
        AG->>AG: re-run gap analysis with answers
    end
    AG->>AG: generate proposal (LLM — Sonnet)
    AG->>FS: write_proposal → data/output/proposal_v1.md
    AG->>S: post proposal to Slack
